    <h1>Accessibility Statement for the AMUNATCOLL Project Website “AMU Natural History Collections Online: Digitization and Sharing of Natural History Data Resources of the Faculty of Biology, Adam Mickiewicz University in Poznań”</h1>

 <p><span id="a11y-podmiot"> The Faculty of Biology at Adam Mickiewicz University in Poznań is committed to ensuring the accessibility of its website in accordance with the provisions of the Act of 4 April 2019 on the digital accessibility of websites and mobile applications of public entities. This accessibility statement applies to the website: <a href="http://anc.amu.edu.pl">anc.amu.edu.pl</a></span></p>
 <p>Website publication date: <span id="a11y-data-publikacja">2020-01-01</span></p><p>Date of last update: <span id="a11y-data-aktualizacja">The website is updated on an ongoing basis as an information site for the AMUNATCOLL project.</span></p>
 <p>Compliance status with the Digital Accessibility Act: <span id="a11y-status">The website is partially compliant with the Act of 4 April 2019 on the digital accessibility of websites and mobile applications of public entities due to the non-compliances or exclusions listed below: </span></p>
 <ul>
 <li>Videos do not contain captions for the hearing impaired.</li>
 <li>Not all images include alternative text descriptions.</li>
 </ul>
 <p>Date of preparation of the Accessibility Statement: <span id="a11y-data-sporzadzenie">2021-11-08 </span>
 <span id="a11y-audytor">The statement was prepared on the basis of a self-assessment conducted by the public entity. </span></p>
 
